msgid "Convert to Index using specified date_format."
msgstr "使用指定的 date_format 转换为 Index。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:3
msgid ""
"Return an Index of formatted strings specified by date_format, which "
"supports the same string format as the python standard library. Details "
"of the string format can be found in `python string format doc "
"<https://docs.python.org/3/library/datetime.html#strftime-and-strptime-"
"behavior>`__."
msgstr ""
"返回由 date_format 指定的格式化字符串组成的 Index，支持与 Python 标准库"
"相同的字符串格式。字符串格式的详细信息可以在 `Python 字符串格式文档 <"
"https://docs.python.org/3/library/datetime.html#strftime-and-strptime-"
"behavior>`__ 中找到。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:8
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Formats supported by the C `strftime` API but not by the python string "
"format doc (such as `\"%R\"`, `\"%r\"`) are not officially supported and "
"should be preferably replaced with their supported equivalents (such as "
"`\"%H:%M\"`, `\"%I:%M:%S %p\"`)."
msgstr ""
"受 C `strftime` API 支持但不受 Python 字符串格式文档支持的格式（例如 `\"%"
"R\"`, `\"%r\"`）并未被官方支持，建议使用受支持的等效格式（例如 `\"%H:%M\""
"`, `\"%I:%M:%S %p\"`）。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:13
msgid ""
"Note that `PeriodIndex` support additional directives, detailed in "
"`Period.strftime`."
msgstr "请注意，`PeriodIndex` 支持额外的指令，详见 `Period.strftime`。"

